# Run Scans Page & Graph Visualizer Implementation Plan

This plan outlines the steps to build a fully functional "Run Scans" feature that allows users to configure, execute, and visualize Active Directory security scans directly from the web interface.

## User Review Required

> [!IMPORTANT]
> - **Dependency Addition**: I will need to install `sigma` and `react-sigma-v2` in the frontend for the graph visualization.
> - **PowerShell Execution**: The scan execution will trigger `Invoke-ADSuiteScan.ps1` with user-defined parameters. Ensure the backend environment has the necessary permissions.
> - **Sigma.js Performance**: For extremely large domains, the graph might require additional optimization (e.g., node grouping or filtering).

