## Verification Plan

### Automated Tests
- `npm test` in the backend to ensure route integrity.
- Browser test: Execute a scan with 1 category selected and verify it completes and shows the graph.

### Manual Verification
1. Open the "New Scan" page.
2. Enter a custom name.
3. Select "Access_Control" category.
4. Click "Run Scan".
5. Verify real-time progress updates appear.
6. Verify results table and graph appear automatically at the bottom.
